# Restaurant Website System — gitignore
#
# Storage policy:
#   - Heavy capture artifacts (screenshots, videos, scroll-frames, motion-frames) are LOCAL ONLY.
#     They can be regenerated anytime via scripts/shoot-template.sh.
#   - Source-of-truth text (source.md, meta/*.json, the audit MDs) IS committed —
#     meta JSON preserves the ground-truth design tokens forever, so a template can be
#     re-recreated from audit + meta even if every screenshot is wiped.
#   - Template public/placeholder/ images ARE committed (small, runtime-needed). Forks
#     replace them with real restaurant photos.

# Heavy capture artifacts — regenerable via scripts/shoot-template.sh
inputs/*/*/screenshots/
inputs/*/*/scroll-frames/
inputs/*/*/videos/
inputs/*/*/motion-frames/

# Recreation sanity screenshots — regenerable by running the template's dev server + screenshot script
templates/*/recreation-screenshots/

# Node / Next.js
node_modules/
.next/
out/
*.tsbuildinfo
.env*.local
.DS_Store
*.log
.vercel

# Playwright caches
.playwright-cache/
